        How GST Applies When Selling Property in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Most established home sales are GST-free, but new builds and some other property types are not. Here is what Queensland sellers need to understand about GST before they list.
      </p>
